Somebody started
saying something.

01:20:21.410 --> 01:20:23.100
Who started saying something?

01:20:23.100 --> 01:20:24.390
OK.

01:20:24.390 --> 01:20:25.900
Any other ideas?

01:20:25.900 --> 01:20:27.230
Breast feeding.

01:20:27.230 --> 01:20:29.560
Who said that?

01:20:29.560 --> 01:20:31.190
Look at that, they
