OK.

01:20:40.214 --> 01:20:41.696
You want to be that way.

01:20:44.660 --> 01:20:48.010
I'm out of here.

01:20:48.010 --> 01:20:48.800
OK.

01:20:48.800 --> 01:20:54.230
So if and only if you read the
