01:20:54.230 --> 01:20:55.060
Yes!

01:20:55.060 --> 01:20:55.990
Breastfeeding.

01:20:55.990 --> 01:20:57.180
OK.

01:20:57.180 --> 01:21:00.560
If and only if you were having
a particular type of diet

01:21:00.560 --> 01:21:02.790
very early in life
that is extremely

01:21:02.790 --> 01:21:05.890
rich in the types
of carbohydrates

01:21:05.890 --> 01:21:07.910
that this enzyme works on.

01:21:07.910 --> 01:21:10.820
So a very dramatic
if and only if there.

01:21:10.820 --> 01:21:12.567
I don't know why I
